Φ(Being-With) = σ(singular|plural) ∘ ρ(exposure|withdrawal) ∘ λ(fusion|coexistence) ∘ β(isolation|community) ∘ δγ(sense|world) ∘ μ(substance|relation) + ε | :naked_with

## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: singular|plural — Coexistence preserves singularity without dissolving it; the plural is not a merger.
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: exposure|withdrawal — Being-with is active openness to others, a capacity to be affected and to respond.
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: fusion|coexistence — Traditional community-as-fusion transforms into coexistence-without-merger.
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: isolation|community — Shared exposure grows community from isolation through relational engagement.
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: sense|world — Sense emerges through shared exposure; the world is structured as sense and sense as world.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: substance|relation — Community is not a substance but a dynamic relational space.

## Z-State
:naked_with — Community stripped of essence or totalizing identity; pure relational coexistence.

